data.description: Discover your dream ranch-style home with 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms including a spacious primary suite, and two car garage. The primary bedroom features a washer and dryer combo in the walk-in closet, and updated bath, adding convenience to luxury. Beautiful updates on the main level add to the appeal of this spacious home. Enjoy two living spaces, each with fireplaces. There's a walkout basement to your backyard oasis. Call/text The Houck team for your private tour 307-462-2622.
